28 August 2008Government will hold Cluster media briefings on the implementation of the Government Programme of Action.The briefings will take place at the Union Buildings, Room 153 and Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town. There will be a video link-up at all briefings.Briefings schedule: Friday, 29 August 2008 10:00 - 11:30: International Relations, Peace and Security (IRPS) Cluster Chair: Deputy Minister Aziz PahadEnquiries Matshepo Seedat (Pretoria) Cell: 083 228 5041Colin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)